Private gsl As New GlauxSoftLib.EvidenceFormCode(Me) Private m_ah As New AddressManagementAddIn.AddressHelper() Private m_Salut As clsAddrAndSolutHelper = Nothing Private m_bInternal As Boolean = True Private m_bIsFetching As Boolean = False Private m_IsNew As Boolean = False
Private Sub frmPerson_ObjectSelected(ByVal sender As Object, _ ByVal e As System.EventArgs) Handles MyBase.ObjectSelected
'--- prüft ob das objekt bereits vorhanden ist Dim sTag As String = GetAgent.GetObjectTag(CurrentObject.ClassID, CurrentObject.ObjectID)
If Len(sTag) = 0 Then m_IsNew = True End If
Try m_bInternal = True m_ah.InitService(cmbCountryCode, cmbCountryName, cmbState, cmbCityCode, cmbCityName, "CountryCode", "CountryName", "CityState", "CityCode", "CityName") If Not m_bIsFetching Then m_bInternal = False
If m_IsNew Then Me.cmbCountryCode.Text = "CH" Me.ObjectChanged(False) End If
'--- Titel dynamisch setzen gsl.setFormCaption()
'--- Beziehungs-Checkbox unsichtbar machen gsl.setRelationCheckboxVisibility(False)
'--- Referenzfelder aufgrund angewähltem Datensatz setzen gsl.setReferenceControls() Catch err As Exception GetPaneBrowser.ShowMessage(MsgBoxStyle.Critical, err.Message) End Try
End Sub
Private Sub frmPerson_On_BeforeFetch( _ ByVal sender As System.Object, _ ByVal e As EventArgs) _ Handles MyBase.On_BeforeFetch
m_bInternal = True m_bIsFetching = True
End Sub
Private Sub frmPerson_On_AfterFetch( _ ByVal sender As System.Object, _ ByVal e As EventArgs) _ Handles MyBase.On_AfterFetch
m_bInternal = False m_bIsFetching = False
End Sub
Private Sub AddressingForm_SelectedIndexChanged( _ ByVal sender As System.Object, _ ByVal e As EventArgs) _ Handles AddressingForm.SelectedIndexChanged
'--- Internal call must be ignored! It is done by setting initial value to be shown If m_bInternal Then Return End If
Dim SolutationName As String If m_Salut Is Nothing Then m_Salut = New clsAddrAndSolutHelper() m_Salut.InitData() End If
If m_Salut.GetSolutationByAddrForm(AddressingForm.SelectedItem, SolutationName) Then '--- if the method has returned TRUE, then there is a respective '--- salutation for the selected addressing form Salutation.SelectedItem = SolutationName End If
End Sub
Private Sub frmPerson_On_BeforeObjectSave( _ ByVal sender As System.Object, _ ByVal e As ObjectSaveEventArg) _ Handles MyBase.On_BeforeObjectSave
m_bInternal = True m_bIsFetching = True
End Sub
Private Sub frmPerson_On_AfterObjectSave( _ ByVal sender As System.Object, _ ByVal e As ObjectSaveEventArg) _ Handles MyBase.On_AfterObjectSave
m_bInternal = False m_bIsFetching = False
End Sub
Private Sub frmPerson_On_Closing( _ ByVal sender As System.Object, _ ByVal e As On_ClosingEventArgs) _ Handles MyBase.On_Closing
m_bInternal = True
End Sub

'--- prüft ob das objekt bereits vorhanden ist Dim sTag As String = GetAgent.GetObjectTag(CurrentObject.ClassID, CurrentObject.ObjectID)
If Len(sTag) = 0 Then m_IsNew = True End If
Try m_bInternal = True m_ah.InitService(cmbCountryCode, cmbCountryName, cmbState, cmbCityCode, cmbCityName, "CountryCode", "CountryName", "CityState", "CityCode", "CityName") If Not m_bIsFetching Then m_bInternal = False
